burn(address).details: Only callable by an EOA to prevent flashloan exploits
burn(address).notice: Burn accrued `_coin` via a preset burner

burn_many(address[20]).details: Only callable by an EOA to prevent flashloan exploits
burn_many(address[20]).notice: Burn accrued admin fees from multiple coins

commit_new_parameters(address,uint256,ui.notice: Commit new parameters for `_pool`, A: `amplification`, fee: `new_fee` and admin fee: `new_admin_fee`

params._new_admin_fee: New admin fee, less than MAX_ADMIN_FEE
params._new_fee_gamma: New fee gamma, within the bounds of [1, 2**100]
params._new_ma_half_time: New MA half time, less than 7 days
params._new_mid_fee: New mid fee, less than or equal to `_new_out_fee`
params._new_out_fee: New out fee, greater than MIN_FEE and less than MAX_FEE

commit_set_admins(address,address,addres.notice: Set ownership admin to `_o_admin`, parameter admin to `_p_admin` and emergency admin to `_e_admin`

commit_transfer_ownership(address,addres.notice: Transfer ownership for `_pool` pool to `new_owner` address

params._pool: Pool which ownership is to be transferred

kill_me(address).notice: Pause the pool `_pool` - only remove_liquidity will be callable

ramp_A_gamma(address,uint256,uint256,uin.notice: Start gradually increasing A and gamma of `_pool` reaching `_future_A` and `_future_gamma` at `_future_time` time

revert_new_parameters(address).notice: Revert comitted new parameters for `_pool` pool

set_aave_referral(address,uint256).notice: Set Aave referral for undelying tokens of `_pool` to `referral_code`

set_donate_approval(address,address,bool.notice: Set approval of `_caller` to donate admin fees for `_pool`

stop_ramp_A_gamma(address).notice: Stop gradually increasing A and gamma of `_pool`

unkill_me(address).notice: Unpause the pool `_pool`, re-enabling all functionality

params._pool: Pool address to withdraw admin fees from

withdraw_many(address[20]).notice: Withdraw admin fees from multiple pools

params._pools: List of pool address to withdraw admin fees from
